      <content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PracticalConversation2">&lt;h3 id=&quot;어떻게-이친구를-알게되었는지-물어볼-때&quot;&gt;어떻게 이친구를 알게되었는지 물어볼 때&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How do you know her?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;어디-출신인지-물어볼-때formal&quot;&gt;어디 출신인지 물어볼 때(formal)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;May I ask you where you`re from?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;그나라의-정확히-어디서-왔는지-물어볼-때&quot;&gt;그나라의 정확히 어디서 왔는지 물어볼 때&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Where in Australia?
Which park of Australia?
Which city of Australia?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;왜-일본에-왔는지-물어볼-때&quot;&gt;왜 일본에 왔는지 물어볼 때&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What brought you to Japan
May I ask you why you come here in Japan&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;살짝웃다&quot;&gt;살짝웃다&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;smirking&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;알고있지만-써먹지-못한-단어들&quot;&gt;알고있지만 써먹지 못한 단어들&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;guest : 손님
glass : 잔
Wear a necklace : 목걸이를 하다&lt;/p&gt;</content>

      
      
      
      
      

